Q: Some information on AutoTools?
A: Here a free book online. http://www.freesoftwaremagazine.com/books/autotools_a_guide_to_autoconf_automake_libtool

Q: WTH, explain the AutoTools structure!
A: Ok, it's something like this:

:
|-- Manoi                               configure.ac    (master)
|   |
:   |-- src                             configure.ac    (src)
    :   :

Every directory which can act as a module has its own configure.ac. It can be used in standalone
fashion.


